{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 290.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for example, the kapo which was the-- the foreman of that group would announce-- usually they were Germans, also inmates, political prisoners or otherwise or thieves or whatever, bandits-- and they would have that job.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would report.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would be the first ones coming out to work and they would say, for example, my kommando was 70.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was a painter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I guess I couldn't make a plumber or they had enough plumbers, so I suddenly become a painter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they-- he would-- he would be in front of the lines and he would say, kommando 70 with 200 people going out to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that-- that total, of course, you had to come back also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they would count just the lines and mingle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and this is how we would march out to work and go into the factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As a painter, we would-- first, we would have those metal brushes and take the rust off steel sheets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know what they were, but they were steel sheets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we would paint them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they'd build those huge gasometers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know what was inside-- could have been oil, could have been gas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But this is what we were doing in building it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "First-- first taking off the rust and then they would build it and then we would paint it again and again and again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always volunteered to work high up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Germans themselves were afraid to climb high.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was young and I could work at my own pace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, I know work had to be done, but I would work at my own pace once I was up there.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
